    • Method Detail

      • incomingMessage

        void incomingMessage​(java.lang.String from,
                     java.util.List<java.lang.String> to,
                     java.lang.String message)
        Called on a general incoming message.
        Parameters:
        from - The node name (hostname) of the sender of the message.
        to - The node(s) (hostname(s)) the message was sent to. A '*' is to all nodes, a Role targets that Role otherwise the node(s) are a comma seperated list of nodes.
        message - The message payload. The format is undefined or defined by the caller implementation.
